REINDEX INDEX CONCURRENTLY t_reindex_idx;
\d+ t_reindex;
                                 Table "public.t_reindex"
 Column  |  Type   | Collation | Nullable | Default | Storage | Stats target | Description 
---------+---------+-----------+----------+---------+---------+--------------+-------------
